   Blood Type / Blood Group
  </title>
  <meta content="Blood Type / Blood Group" property="og:title"/>
  <meta content="Blood type or blood group is the classification of blood based on antigens on surface of RBCs.  Four main blood types/groups - A, B, AB, O. Cross matching tests compatibility of the donor, recipient blood." name="Description"/>
